Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:20.89,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}いざ征け 光あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:30.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA Ah Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:36.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA Ah Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:54.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}星間に行く砦は唯一の安息地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:02:00.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}焦燥に打ち震え 所以には生と死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:05.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA Ah Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:11.08,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:19.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}此所へいざ集わんと 導かれしは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:25.32,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}志携えて 立ち向かえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:31.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}衛り継ぐ愛と 輝け命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:39.68,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}果敢に進む我ら シドニアの騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:20.89,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}踏上征途 光芒与我们同在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:54.30,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}穿梭星际的堡垒是唯一的安息之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:02:00.39,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}颤抖因焦躁而激发 生死于因果中存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:19.03,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}齐聚此地 接受引导
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:25.32,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}众志成城 携手迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:31.72,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}满怀薪火相传的爱与灿烂的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:39.68,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}希德尼娅的骑士果敢前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:36.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}あぁ 朽ちていく世界ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:40.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}散りゆく運命ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:45.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}何を信じて生きればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:51.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}そう 君と出逢わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.33,0:22:54.80,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この胸を引き裂くような
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:23:00.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}痛みなんて知らなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:05.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}空の彼方 鳴り響いた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.77,0:23:08.66,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}拙い鎮魂歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.77,0:23:08.66,ED,NTP,80,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}レクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:12.81,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}それでもまだ探している
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:15.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}不確かな現実から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:15.90,ED,NTP,95,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}いま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.38,0:23:18.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}君のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:21.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}巡り逢えた歓びも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.99,0:23:25.58,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}消えていった温もりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.73,0:23:29.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部覚えてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:32.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}愛してたから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:36.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}芽生えていく感情も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:40.40,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}胸に残る傷跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:44.55,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部抱えて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.88,0:23:51.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この道を歩いて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:36.53,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}倘若世界将要腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:40.10,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}如果注定难逃死灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:45.10,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}此生究竟该相信什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:51.10,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是的 如果不曾与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.33,0:22:54.80,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我便不必体会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:23:00.73,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}这撕心裂肺的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:05.43,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}响彻在宇宙彼岸的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.77,0:23:08.66,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是那稚拙的镇魂之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:12.81,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:15.90,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}依然从飘乎的现实中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.38,0:23:18.25,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}找寻你的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:21.85,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}相逢的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.99,0:23:25.58,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}消散的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.73,0:23:29.83,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都历历在目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:32.87,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}因为曾经深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:36.63,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}萌生的情愫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:40.40,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}残留的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:44.55,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.88,0:23:51.48,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}一路前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要文化遗产调查？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个 这到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.51,0:00:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不能在规定时间内完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种景点怎么可能有任务嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想约我去玩就直说好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是去玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是很认真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那 跟我一起接受这个任务吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风很诚心地请伊札那和他去两天一夜的旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是去千秋乡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是千秋乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 凑近一点看更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.28,0:01:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊…伊札那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.98,title,NTP,0,0,0,,任 务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知各修理班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总监命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先使用资材仓库中所保存的建材及装甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 大部分补好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 䌷你今天一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是孤单寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我随时都可以跟你掌位哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弦打 你真是有够下流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 不能搭理这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟我一起飞飞看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请手下留情哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你抓牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弦打！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长 长道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是要调查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是希德尼娅最棒的赏樱胜地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 扶手没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是那边了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了啦 不用装成是在调查的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地板连接处正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 我查到潜入千秋乡的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地图我发给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你帮忙的事也写在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能让他们在千秋乡两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可是定期检查的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被褥 无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查这种地方做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着就是确认防护门的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不安分点是不会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都想看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 得调查才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防护门 运作正常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一项是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在千秋乡待命到明天10:00为止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说待在这里就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 就这点？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我哪知道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个水池明明是无重力的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水却没有飞出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是水池啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是 这是浴池
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫无重力环境专用浴池
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是非常奢侈的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…我们来泡一泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次真想把䌷也带上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟她喜欢泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起来泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这字…是奶奶的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛痛痛痛痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些全都是奶奶教你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险 伊札那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等 听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道你根本不在乎我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.99,eyecatch,NTP,1050,0,0,,希德尼娅百景　千秋乡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:06.00,eyecatch,NTP,994,0,0,,希德尼娅百景　外周壁居住区屋檐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实仔细想想 两个人单独出去过夜也不一定就会发生什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说谷风和伊札那在我们住进来之前就是两个人住的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是那时候伊札那还没开始女性化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然说不要潜入千秋乡的是䌷你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就别再介意了 快睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缬小姐你不也是介意得睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缬小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风先生会不会也请我去那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:10:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 那时我听到他们说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道你根本不在乎我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是呢 谷风是怎么回答的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是觉得偷听是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 缬小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请忘了刚才的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那先这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日凌晨 希德尼娅已进入雷姆星系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz357.4\pos(624,184)}终于进入雷姆星系！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz357.4\pos(738,506)}将加强战时供给管制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部随之宣布将提升警戒态势
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及加强战时供给管制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于走到这一步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真的是希德尼娅现在该走的路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移民到行星七号的人怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然无法取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十有八九…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行星九号我们无论如何都必须拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能拿下这里将决定战局的走向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗行星作为天然要害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将在与大众合船交战时成为重要据点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在先给我争取点时间啊 小林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}第三特编班 卫人用高速自主支援装甲的……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 它在分离状态下也能冲进大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划在对行星九号进行侦察的同时也测试测试这部「隼风」的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是对奇居子发动自杀式攻击用的棺材嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芯的前端还周到地装上了人工颖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这些有一堆替补的操纵士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开着这东西往大众合船里冲就行了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 少说两句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 这次的侦察任务把她搞得有点神经质
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 就算我是总司令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会为了区区一次侦察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就动用那边那种昂贵的最新机型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和像你这样的精英吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅就拜托你了啊 英雄大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想看到王牌纠结的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫纳豆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我是科户濑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说本来明天要出侦察任务的人抗命被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就换我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二套装备换得太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侦察任务也是实战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别给我撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第4第5工作台 快往后移
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别妨碍搬运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准惯性控制机关的最终检查可别偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击装备检查 确认已更换为第二套装备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击装备确认无误后 操纵士开始上机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侦察队的机体与隼风连接后立即前往行星九号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我方无法观测的区域进行侦察
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后迅速回航希德尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侦察队 出击准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行星九号侦察部队 已出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着准备射出隼风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侦察队 开始掌位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维持现有队形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎喷射防护壁 关闭准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央发射口 隔离壁全部打开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驻座悬吊装置 固定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射口 通道正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高速自主支援装甲「隼风」 出击准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼风 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}隼风 开始引导侦察队向掌位中心靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科户濑 你太靠内了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维持掌位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行速度同步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼风 减速至可连结速度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将到达接触点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向与侦察队同步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谨慎行事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对速度微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼风 装甲打开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侦察队与隼风 飞行速度已同步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始连结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 慢慢靠过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侦察队 维持掌位态势接近隼风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体连结成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连结已成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向 行星九号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大动力前进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇定点啊 谷风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是第一次待命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心情可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就是在这儿急也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去散散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好担心伊札那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想和她一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侦察队报告总司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将进入行星九号背面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇居子很擅长藏身 万事小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正通过星环附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,截至目前一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科户濑 新雷达上有什么反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我这里也没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远看明明那么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近看起来就只是一堆脏兮兮的石头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且感觉奇居子随时可能从阴影里跳出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是平静不下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别光顾着星环了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要到达距行星九号的最近点了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科户濑 怎么了？看到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那 慢慢把意识移回雷达上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航路前方出现了一团雾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾？什么都看不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射希格斯粒子炮试试
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可视化的奇居子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 准备闪避！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标太大了 来不及回避
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么冲过去的话或许能把它打穿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侦察队 放弃隼风 迅速闪避
